OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start with isolated
OL,6,Ffog patches. Sunny spells developing
OL,7,Ffor a while, but cloud slowly bubbling
OL,8,Fup allowing showers to develop by
OL,9,Flunchtime. The showers may become
OL,10,Fheavy and possibly thundery during the
OL,11,Fafternoon. Lighter winds than of late.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDaytime showers easing this
OL,14,Fevening leaving a dry night with clear
OL,15,Fspells. Turning chilly with a patchy
OL,16,Ffrost, before further cloud arrives in
OL,17,Fthe far west by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
